Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嫁过来的时候经过了北边的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕 是那时附上的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么时候被衣棉上染上了一滴绿色的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs17}(被衣:罩在头上的东西。)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我婚礼后才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来是很不祥的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二年我生下第一个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个长子渡彦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从长出斑开始就不断衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次看到这斑我就想起那污点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 我想错了请你原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子 是以人的姿态出生的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连禽兽的样子都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵胞子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那以后不足三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我又被叫到那家去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了你的信 还来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快到家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我答应了要按你的话做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系 多亏你通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 没想到居然迅速到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 成长的速度快得可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子 是以人的姿态出生的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这以后的 由我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那连禽兽的姿态都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连哭声都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绿色的 不知是何物的块
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西一瞬间就钻入地板下 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子本想要个强壮的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但想来是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愉快的日子持续下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 过了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从地板下传出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁抛弃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那时的孩子 我们的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那以后终于长成人的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我内心很害怕 但还是深信了这事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…渡彦的成长很快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吃新鲜的小鱼和果实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到半年就长到了三岁左右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 智力还和婴儿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有表情 也没说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 他长得和我们越来越像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就渐渐对他有了感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时一样 地板下又有婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和渡彦一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得像养他一样养
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定 还会再增加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种可怕的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预感成了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡彦每半年就像涌出来一样的增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我把地板下挖了好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么奇怪的东西也没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:07:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到了今年 长子的情况就渐渐变得奇怪起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天大半都在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色的疹子越长越多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生说是没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后听说有您这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我们虫师也没办法救这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是寿命尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有叫“绵吐”的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外形像绿色的棉花 在空中漂浮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入孕妇胎内 让卵寄生在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生出来的时候是淤泥状
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以很快的速度钻入地板或天花板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了一年后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长成婴儿模样的“人茸”会回到人类的父母身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后的增长方法基本与记录无异
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 但谨慎起见能让我看看地板下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 用不着灯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 而且还有相当的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是绵吐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 不是什么也没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太阳光下好好看看这土
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人茸的身体与虫的本体以像线一样的东西相连
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们不过是为了向本体输送养分的虫的一部分而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子即将完成使命而坏死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且将死之际会从体内吐出大量“种子”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要在这之前杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 你以为我们为什么才叫你来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把那孩子从那叫虫还是什么东西的手里救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有要救的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子只是披着你们孩子的皮的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们就是杀了你们本该出生的孩子的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们理解这点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 要恨就恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难为你说服你妻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是到现在也不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都养了三年多 也没什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 请无论如何别把其他的孩子从我手里夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这以后请睁一只眼闭一只眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子长疹子前什么坏处也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次子和他之后出生的孩子我都会在吐出种子之前杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵吐的寿命从十年到三十年不等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还不知道这种状态要持续到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也根本不知道你到底得杀多少个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那个很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此也想继续养吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想让内人伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:11:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明将剩下的四个也叫做渡彦 用心抚养
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失去了所有的孩子 不知道会变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前曾嫁到山对面镇子里经营大店铺的人家里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里曾不负众望 生下了继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在未满周岁的时候因些小事而把那孩子害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因此被对方抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么会这样 太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止 只要知道是“绵吐的孩子”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎都马上全杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此连根也都枯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有让不知道何时会带来危险的第二个活下来的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法断言那些东西在这以后不会发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜欢 不知道就全部杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种粗枝大叶的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能在分开后一直在这里监视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个月内我还会回来看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题给我写信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受您恩惠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而信 不足三个月就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会被杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡彦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内人的话 总算是理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续抚养异物… 只要遵守这个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 银古来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎前来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是躺着好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 不知道该怎么道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到事情结束为止\N我不把那家伙从寝室里放出来 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为她理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说事情发生了变化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我本来打算马上说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子并不只是成长加快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只教过次子剥栗子壳的方法 四子却在剥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次子好不容易才记住 他却看着就会了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是慢慢有了智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被雨淋湿了 马上给你拿换的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹 肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 这孩子说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 是吗 马上做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这期间 次子开始出现症状
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太早了 上个孩子不是才刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做不行 这家伙是…我们该解决的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹 我怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别杀我 救救我 我还想活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经完全变成像人一样的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我孩子的仇人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说已经是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 开始有思考能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 本来也有这种机能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是由于长子的死而察觉到了危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是 一人得到情报后传播给全员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人都是与根相连的全体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家同时得到五人份的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成长迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是“像人一样的东西”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栖息在他们之中的只是刚会思考的茸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须保护种子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,词语记着但是忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种子 保护种子的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是能起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次子在里屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后 我要锄掉根 把剩下的“孩子”们带走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能再把那些东西交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 别杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们吃人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我们比较强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要让你们连种子也不剩地死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙想把地板下的根全烧掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 难道你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带来的书卷上写着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来无意识间应该能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护种子只能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡彦 那些孩子在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些家伙放的火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们为了种子什么都会做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙就是这种虫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经是我的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡彦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡彦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡彦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡彦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根完全烧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵吐是一察觉到大危险来临就会把人茸从根切离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只让种子逃到外面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人茸改变姿态进入长眠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什么时候能再生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是你们死后也难说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之在那到来前就由你们保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不离身地带着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给了他们什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矿物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是我生活食粮的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亏本买卖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匪夷所思的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮得到你说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没进入睡眠啊 以前的记录明明是那么记载的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我不困
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不趁现在把我杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你寿命未尽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匪夷所思的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 你快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

